Title: Viagem para Portugal
DateModified: '2019-02-27'
DatePublished: '2019-02-27'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/viagem-para-portugal
SetInCountry: India
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Rajashri  Hapse
AuthorCountry: India
Text: '"Magnifico !", I uttered when I first landed in Portugal. Little did I know
  this is going to be amazing opportunity to witness the beauty of this country .
  The trip was unplanned and honesty didn''t expected it to be so mesmerizing ...
  I always dreamt of visiting Portugal to explore the culture, cuisine, music, and
  places, etc. I hope the viagem further will be much more interesting and one to
  remember of , let''s travel and make memories with this country hence the name of
  my title ''Viagem para Portugal''.'
